be imposed and the form of licences, certificates, permits
and  approvals;

(c) prescribing the standards or grades of oil palm products
and making provision for giving effect to such standards
and grades, including provisions for or relating to labelling;

(g) providing for the registration of contracts relating to the
sale and purchase of oil palm products and the details of
such  contracts;
